                           type="illustration" unit="mm">
                           <height>111</height>
                           <width>83</width>
                        </dimensions><p> The cat seizes a mouse.</p></item>
                        <item>Folio <locus from="4b">4b,</locus><dimensions
                           type="illustration" unit="mm">
                           <height>150</height>
                           <width>93</width>
                        </dimensions><p> The cat repents in the mosque for killing the mouse.</p></item>
                        <item>Folio <locus from="5a">5a,</locus><dimensions
                           type="illustration" unit="mm">
                           <height>25</height>
                           <width>38</width>
                        </dimensions><p> A mouse reports back that the cat has repented.</p></item>
                        <item>Folio <locus from="5b">5b,</locus><dimensions
                           type="illustration" unit="mm">
                           <height>96</height>
                           <width>81</width>
                        </dimensions><p> A delegation of seven mice brings gifts to the repentant cat.</p></item>
                        <item>Folio <locus from="6a">6a,</locus><dimensions
                           type="illustration" unit="mm">
                           <height>108</height>
                           <width>103</width>
                        </dimensions><p> The cat kills five of the mice but two escape.</p></item>
                        <item>Folio <locus from="7b">7b,</locus><dimensions
                           type="illustration" unit="mm">
                           <height>148</height>
                           <width>108</width>
                        </dimensions><p> The king of the mice assembles his army.</p></item>
                        <item>Folio <locus from="8b">8b,</locus><dimensions
