                           <height>112</height>
                           <width>97</width>
                        </dimensions><p> The captive cat is brought before the king of the mice.</p></item>
                        <item>Folio <locus from="9b">9b,</locus><dimensions
                           type="illustration" unit="mm">
                           <height>68 </height>
                           <width>103</width>
                        </dimensions><p> The vizier of the mice accompanies the cat on horseback.</p></item>
                        <item>Folio <locus from="10a">10a,</locus><dimensions
                           type="illustration" unit="mm">
                           <height>103 </height>
                           <width>85</width>
                        </dimensions><p> The vizier of the mice is slaughtered by the cats.</p></item>
                        <item>Folio <locus from="11a">11a,</locus><dimensions
                           type="illustration" unit="mm">
                           <height>124</height>
                           <width>114</width>
                        </dimensions><p> The army of the mice captures the cat.</p></item>
